# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [0.1.0-alpha] - 2019-04-02
- Initial alpha release

## [0.1.0-alpha.1] - 2019-04-04
- Fix major bugs preventing library import/require due to a build failure
- Use developit/microbundle instead of parcel to ensure builds are properly structured for library use
- Restructure state/layout/render setup to avoid circular dependency warnings

## [0.1.0-alpha.2] - 2019-04-05
- Use webpack instead to have more control over the build process

## [0.1.0-alpha.3] - 2019-06-17
- Fix offset bug
- Add local time style differentiator
- Fix lib build output
